==English==

===Pronunciation===
kwarts

===Noun===
'''quartz'''  (''plural:'' '''[[quartzs]]''')
# Quartz is the most abundant [[mineral]] on the earth's surface.  It occurs in a variety of forms, both [[crystal]]line and [[amorphous]].  Found in every environment.  There is a complete article at [[Wikipedia:Quartz]]. 

*Chemical composition: Silicon dioxide, <math>SiO_2</math>

